02:40:00.319 --> 02:40:06.785
I'm trying to shake you to reality that there's many people that thought they had tomorrow.

02:40:06.786 --> 02:40:21.999
Statistically, I think they say 170,000 or 175,000 people a day die around the world.

02:40:22.000 --> 02:40:45.279
I wonder how many of them thought they had tomorrow, but they died today on the way to work or on the way home—174,000 average.

02:40:45.280 --> 02:40:50.478
When is our number up? We don't know. I pray every day that he protects me.

02:40:50.479 --> 02:40:58.639
I pray every day that with long life he satisfies me and I believe it.

02:40:58.640 --> 02:41:11.476
But don't gamble with your eternity if you don't know him. It's appointed unto man once to die and after that to judgment.

02:41:11.477 --> 02:41:19.839
If you're here tonight, even if there's just one of you, he leaves the 99 to go after the one.

02:41:19.840 --> 02:41:26.719
You say to me, 'Brandon, I just want to make sure I'm right with the Lord.

02:41:26.720 --> 02:41:33.728
I just want to make sure I'm all in.'I want to say a simple prayer with you.

02:41:33.729 --> 02:41:55.519
You have to mean it with your heart. First you have to believe that he is.

02:41:55.520 --> 02:42:03.199
And I believe if right now you feel that tugging on your heart, that's the Holy Spirit.

02:42:03.200 --> 02:42:10.799
No man comes to the Father unless he's calling him. He's calling you right now.

02:42:10.800 --> 02:42:19.443
So I'm going to say a simple prayer. Say it with me. 'Jesus, I believe you're the Son of God.

02:42:19.444 --> 02:42:29.556
I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day. I'm a sinner and I want you to be my Lord and personal Savior.

02:42:29.557 --> 02:42:37.919
I ask you to forgive me of my sins. I ask you to forgive me of all my unrighteousness.

02:42:37.920 --> 02:42:44.128
From this day forward, Lord, I turn my back on the world. I turn my back on the devil.

02:42:44.129 --> 02:42:54.488
I turn my back on my sin. And from this day forward, Lord, I'll serve you with all my heart.

02:42:54.489 --> 02:43:01.796
I'll make you my Lord and personal Savior. Thank you, Lord. I'm sold out to you right now.

02:43:01.797 --> 02:43:08.994
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life. Thank you, Lord, that I'm free from my sin.

02:43:08.995 --> 02:43:16.049
Thank you, Lord, that today is a fresh, clean start. I dedicate my life to you, Lord.

02:43:16.050 --> 02:43:35.438
From this day forward, I'm sold out to you. I'll be a light for you in the darkness, a light that shines bright everywhere I go.

02:43:35.439 --> 02:43:39.891
Thank you, Lord, that you've forgiven me. Thank you from this day forward, Lord.

02:43:39.892 --> 02:43:53.919
I'll be with you in paradise if I was to die. Thank you, Lord, in Jesus'name. Amen and amen.'I believe it's just a simple prayer.

02:43:53.920 --> 02:44:01.839
The moment you confess your sins, he is faithful and just to forgive you of your sins and cleanse you of all unrighteousness.

02:44:01.840 --> 02:44:08.483
And I believe the moment you did that, as far as the east is from the west, he doesn't remember it anymore.

02:44:08.484 --> 02:44:15.644
You say, 'Well, Brandon, what do I do now?'You find a Bible-believing, non-denominational church.

02:44:15.645 --> 02:44:21.355
Get a Bible and read your Bible every single day. Pray with us.

02:44:21.356 --> 02:44:27.358
Get plugged into a local church wherever you are in your area. Find a non-denominational church.

02:44:27.359 --> 02:44:32.215
Go there and tell them, "Listen, I just got born again watching a YouTube video.

02:44:32.216 --> 02:44:39.629
I need to be water-baptized."Get water-baptized. Go to church on Sundays and Wednesdays, whenever they have the doors open.

02:44:39.630 --> 02:44:47.944
Learn about Christianity and listen to that preacher. Get filled up with the word of God; it will change you from the inside out.

02:44:47.945 --> 02:44:54.948
I'm telling you. You say, "Well, that old book."Oh, no. This book is alive, and the more you read it, it will change you.

02:44:54.949 --> 02:45:03.634
You've got to get this word down inside of you. Now, if you don't have a Bible, I want to buy you your first Bible.

02:45:03.635 --> 02:45:10.478
If you just got born again tonight through our ministry here, we want to buy you your first Bible.

02:45:10.479 --> 02:45:17.757
That's what my wife's working on right now: getting the Bibles out to people. You have to give us your address.

02:45:17.758 --> 02:45:26.079
You can't just email me and say, "Hey, I got saved."I have to know who you are, where you come from, and how I can send you your Bible.

02:45:26.080 --> 02:45:30.979
And so, we will send you a Bible if you tell us your address. There's a lot.

02:45:30.980 --> 02:45:37.681
Diana goes, "Brandon, there's so many emails where they just tell me, 'Hey, I got saved,'and they have their name."You've got to tell me your address.

02:45:37.682 --> 02:45:43.009
You've got to say, "Hey, I live at this place."We won't bother you ever again.

02:45:43.010 --> 02:45:47.895
We're not here to solicit you. We'll never ask you for a dime.

02:45:47.896 --> 02:45:55.199
Our heart is always to give and just to tell you Jesus loves you and He has a plan for your life.

02:45:55.200 --> 02:46:02.994
Now, we have places down there if you feel led to do things—that's on you—but I'm never going to ask you for anything. Never.

02:46:02.995 --> 02:46:11.129
Now, there are people that say, "Brandon, I want to be a blessing to you because I'd like to give you a coffee or something."That's because God led you to.

02:46:11.130 --> 02:46:14.354
Like I said, I've never asked for anything on here and never will.

02:46:14.355 --> 02:46:18.857
So if you have somebody saying, "Hey, I'm asking you for something,"they're a liar.

02:46:18.858 --> 02:46:25.481
We've never done it and we will never do it. Freely we've been given, and freely we give.

02:46:25.482 --> 02:46:35.438
We love you and we pray for you. Now, there are scammers out there trying to make my voice say AI things.

02:46:35.439 --> 02:46:42.722
I'm not saying some of the stuff they're saying; they have AI using my voice.

02:46:42.723 --> 02:46:51.981
These are scammers. If it's not on my YouTube channel, do not follow it. We're taking these people down as best as we can.

02:46:51.982 --> 02:47:01.436
We have new scammers coming up every single day copying my videos, and some of them have 100,000 or 150,000 views. And it's not me.

02:47:01.438 --> 02:47:12.239
Some of you go, "Brandon, you're over here saying this."I say, "I never said any of that."If it's not on my channel, it is not in the description.

02:47:12.240 --> 02:47:19.275
My X account, my Instagram, my Facebook—all of it is in the description below.

02:47:19.276 --> 02:47:25.631
Click those links and you won't be scammed by impersonators. Don't donate any money to them.

02:47:25.632 --> 02:47:30.959
I don't ask you for a dime for crypto; I don't give advice—none of this stuff.

02:47:30.960 --> 02:47:34.804
They are ripping people off and I'm just trying to protect you.

02:47:34.805 --> 02:47:39.577
Everything is in the link description below. That's how you get a hold of me, my email, everything.

02:47:39.578 --> 02:47:43.919
And we just want to love on y'all. God bless you for coming tonight.

02:47:43.920 --> 02:47:51.066
All 55 of you that gave your heart to Jesus Christ, welcome to the family.

02:47:51.067 --> 02:47:59.077
There'll be many more throughout the week, however long they watch this video until it goes dead in the algorithm.

02:47:59.078 --> 02:48:07.119
I always laugh about it because it only takes about two or three days and they start to die.

02:48:07.120 --> 02:48:16.585
YouTube only promotes it for as long as you like and comment on it.

02:48:16.586 --> 02:48:26.620
It's the likes and the comments that keep it alive in the algorithm. After about two or three weeks, it's dead.

02:48:26.621 --> 02:48:34.693
So, hopefully the message got out for whoever needed it, and then we bring it back with shorts and stuff.

02:48:34.694 --> 02:48:38.751
It's work, but we're so thankful for every single one of you that came tonight.

02:48:38.752 --> 02:48:45.713
We had 7,900 people here right now—unless a lot of you left during the altar call—but we love y'all.

02:48:45.714 --> 02:48:49.875
We're so excited that you come out and pray with us every time.

02:48:49.876 --> 02:48:56.274
It's such a blessing. I believe many hands make light work. Isn't it wonderful?

02:48:56.275 --> 02:49:01.985
Jesus is wonderful, and we give all the glory to Him. We attract to deflect.

02:49:01.986 --> 02:49:16.159
I say it again, like sister Kathryn Kuhlman would say, "I didn't use Him; He uses me."I'm just a vessel, and He could use any one of you.

02:49:16.160 --> 02:49:21.679
I'm just a person just like you are. I'm so thankful that He would use me today.

02:49:21.680 --> 02:49:27.677
We love y'all. Thank you for coming out. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:49:27.678 --> 02:49:36.510
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you. God bless you and we'll see you again soon. Bye-bye.

